This is a fork of vitunes. Just a few minor tweaks that made this a little
more useful for me. The diff follows below. Basically I added key bindings
for a "next song" function and an external file-based interface so I could
use hotkeys to control vitunes. The makefile was only modified to help it
compile on Mac OS X.

